""SELECT `s1`.`Id`, `s1`.`CreatedAt`, `s1`.`CreatedById`, `s1`.`Name`, `s2`.`SessionId`, `s2`.`UserId`, `s2`.`Id`, `s2`.`Avatar`, `s2`.`Email`, `s2`.`Password`, `s2`.`Username`, `s3`.`Id`, `s3`.`CreatedAt`, `s3`.`Description`, `s3`.`PaidById`, `s3`.`SessionId`, `s3`.`TotalAmount`, `s3`.`Id0`, `s3`.`Amount`, `s3`.`ExpenseId`, `s3`.`Status`, `s3`.`UserId`
FROM (
    SELECT `s`.`Id`, `s`.`CreatedAt`, `s`.`CreatedById`, `s`.`Name`
    FROM `Sessions` AS `s`
    WHERE `s`.`Id` = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS `s1`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `s0`.`SessionId`, `s0`.`UserId`, `u`.`Id`, `u`.`Avatar`, `u`.`Email`, `u`.`Password`, `u`.`Username`
    FROM `Sessionusers` AS `s0`
    INNER JOIN `Users` AS `u` ON `s0`.`UserId` = `u`.`Id`
) AS `s2` ON `s1`.`Id` = `s2`.`SessionId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `e`.`Id`, `e`.`CreatedAt`, `e`.`Description`, `e`.`PaidById`, `e`.`SessionId`, `e`.`TotalAmount`, `e0`.`Id` AS `Id0`, `e0`.`Amount`, `e0`.`ExpenseId`, `e0`.`Status`, `e0`.`UserId`

    LEFT JOIN `ExpenseSplits` AS `e0` ON `e`.`Id` = `e0`.`ExpenseId`
